cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI 

The paper focuses on sponsored search in e-commerce, which involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning techniques such as neural networks (LG). The proposed framework also involves natural language processing (CL) and image processing (CV) to retrieve and rank relevant ads. Additionally, the optimization of the pointwise cross-entropy loss is a common objective in machine learning (AI) for ranking tasks.
